objections.suggested_fix:
Add validation:
```javascript
var validThemes = ['dark', 'light'];
if (!t || validThemes.indexOf(t) === -1) t = 'dark';
```
Use const/let with IIFE scoping for consistency.

All durations must be set to 0ms or 1ms in reduced-motion context:
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  :root {
    --duration-fast: 0ms;
    --duration-normal: 0ms;
    --duration-slow: 0ms;
    --duration-glacial: 0ms;
  }
}
```

Import synchronously at top of file and use conditional plugin inclusion:
```javascript
import { visualizer } from 'rollup-plugin-visualizer';
const plugins = [react({ jsxRuntime: 'automatic' })];
if (analyzeMode) plugins.push(visualizer({...}));
```

Use a dedicated focus inner-ring token that adapts to context, or use single-ring with forced contrast:
```css
*:focus-visible {
  outline: 3px solid var(--color-focus-ring-solid);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```
This is simpler and WCAG-compliant via offset.

